{"tid":1902444,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"舖頭有個老屎忽成日玩針對，好想辭職","createTime":"2020-02-28T10:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:33:20.000Z","uid":306876,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62b0bc87e968f62d5be8c7fdd5c4f20ba58b17f8","tid":1902444,"uid":306876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:33:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟上年入左間舖頭做partime <br />\n入面有件有屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開始未熟個陣教我都幾有耐性又詳細下，但我學野慢加上又新，有啲位5熟悉做錯左，咁一開始佢只係提醒同教翻我，之後熟落左就直接鬧9我，有時係小小事都鬧到我9彩好似世界末日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見我好似有啲5開心5出聲呢，就會話以前我學校啲老師都係咁鬧我，仲嚇我話會肥佬我添<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以前比人鬧得仲慘丫」 咁樣氹返我 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開始呢個原因我傻仲會受下嘅，但呢幾個月開始，又會開我玩笑，係傷到我人格同扺毁我工作能力嗰種玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又點我做野，例如明明佢翻夜更，早更叫夜更搞埋件事佢，結果佢直接推比我呢個5洗翻夜晚嘅人，叫我朝早記得得一定要搞掂丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個種語氣呢~~完全就係5好5記得呢個係我嘅責任咁，問點解係我，就話「我5想做」再笑幾下，我真係笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時其他人做野甩漏，沒汁野沒fill野，咁啱早更我有份翻，夜更我拍住佢翻，佢見到啲野咁那西但其實5關我事5係我日頭負責嘅area都懶左我先，總之一定係我錯架啦～鬧9我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我又5知咩事，佢又話我沒記性，錯啲咩都5記得，好彩之後有人出聲話5關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係其他人問題，件事根本5關我事，之後佢淨係識同個個人講左聲你以後5再犯啦，再同我講聲sor囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢啲野仲要一星期黎幾次。。我而家都5新，啲野都上手左好多，但一有問題一有錯總係懶9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />5會諗會5會係其他新人嘅問題(翻1-3個月)有錯鬧正常，屌佢我沒錯都屈9我有錯，好難頂lor<br />\n但我先翻得半年，人地翻左就10年啦，鬥5過丫"},{"pid":"fdeb2334ad973644755b30b72af660d1c754de5c","tid":1902444,"uid":115910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"見到你啲icon都想屌柒你"},{"pid":"349ce4b18038d9439c6212c658c90c09b97c540f","tid":1902444,"uid":221478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:35:05.000Z","msg":"5你老母"},{"pid":"ad1602b47623af8e18ea6f8a44bbf0774d8f40f7","tid":1902444,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"辭啦"},{"pid":"024a2e89c089f2161441840243a34bd586cd95b5","tid":1902444,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ced028777857599deb219e2270a95ee1d586d68","tid":1902444,"uid":132249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦小學雞"},{"pid":"eae8d808020cca5cb285edc77d46a76ffeac3e0b","tid":1902444,"uid":67765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"pt wfc"}]}